{"tid":1544398,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY呢個時勢仲落TVB廣告係咩心態？","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T08:10:59.000Z","uid":181330,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"79b078344def372bb80b832fa204db570cd00735","tid":1544398,"uid":181330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"我身為任天堂死忠, 由當年PS1, 玩到PSV, 再到而家嘅PS4 pro都買。<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知你居然係TVB落廣告... 你知唔知TVB係幾咁偏頗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我一直支持既SONY會喺咁, 我真係覺得痛心疾首, 強烈要求撤回廣告! <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你決定繼續落TVB廣告, 我以後都唔會再幫襯SONY!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢市場部係咪食撚錯藥？目標客群係邊個都仲未搞得清楚？今時今日仲落廣告去人見人憎嘅假新聞維穩機器CCTVB？有無人可以答我點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁樣係咪要同我地香港年輕一代割席？真係好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呼籲連登仔一齊幫手去佢fb屌撚醒佢，我真係唔想因為CCTVB而放棄一路以來陪住我地呢代人一齊成長，俾我地喺呢個令人窒息嘅社會暫時忘憂嘅夥伴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會阻你地好耐...<br />\n1. 俾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sonyhongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsonyhongkong%2F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWB5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=38a0bd07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sonyhongkong/</a><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\nP. S. 如果可以貼埋自己SONY產品嘅相去留言就效果更佳!!"},{"pid":"85c8a396642f3a7163e777ee06e2812c8cff5e98","tid":1544398,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n(歡迎遲到，好過無到) <br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWB5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=4771f731\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗(<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"ad81763f9c89a77c1edc046a30874fb02327ecd7","tid":1544398,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited